data.description: Welcome to Easy Living in this Fully renovated 2 Bedroom home featuring a New Eat In Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Center Island, Stainless Steel Appliances, Gas Stove, New Porcelain flooring throughout.  New designer full bathroom, Living room, New Boiler and HWW, Sunny Living Room, fenced front and rear yards. Roof replaced in 2015 and the home is newly insulated. Bonus rooms include a rear office which can be used as a den or panty or guest room which leads to the boiler room and out to the back yard and a fully finished attic. Imagine being nearby Rockaway Beach, Shopping, schools, public transportation and having privacy for entertaining, BBQ.
